JAJA, i took care of my teeth so much when i was a kid i could spend 3 days without cleaning them and the dentist will still say i have perfect teeth.

then we went to the dentist to get our teeths checked and while my cousin got told to continue brushing, the dentist told me that i have beautiful white teeth and congratulated me for them.

everyone was so jealous.
